        <div class="text-right" style="    padding: 10px 10px;">
            <h6 style="background-image: url(https://www.sdf.gov.az/development/img/widget-bg.png);background-repeat: repeat-x;background-position: bottom left;padding: 8px 0 23px;position: relative;"><a href="https://www.sdf.gov.az/az//generic/menu/Detail/97/menu" style="    color: #656565;"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-align-right" aria-hidden="true" style="    font-size: 12px;"></span> Fondun Nizamnaməsi</a></h6>
